<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to Our E-Learning Platform</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our E-Learning Platform, {{username}}!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you join our e-learning platform. You now have access to a wide range of courses and resources to help you achieve your learning goals.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need support, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Happy learning!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
